{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 54,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَمَرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qamar",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Moon",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 55,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4847,
        "text": "复活时临近了，月亮破裂了。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4848,
        "text": "如果他们看见一种迹象，他们就退避，而且说：这是一种有力的魔术。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4849,
        "text": "他们否认他，而且顺从私欲。每一件事都是确定的。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4850,
        "text": "包含警戒的许多消息，确已来临他们了，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4851,
        "text": "那是极精密的智慧；但警告是无效的，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4852,
        "text": "故你应当避开他们。当召唤者召人于难事的日子，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4853,
        "text": "他们不敢仰视地由坟中出来，好象是遍地的蝗虫；",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4854,
        "text": "大家引颈而奔，群集于召唤者的面前。不信道的人们将说：这是一个烦难的日子！",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4855,
        "text": "在他们之前，努哈的宗族否认过，他们否认过我的仆人，他们说：这是一个疯人。他曾被喝斥，",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4856,
        "text": "故他祈祷他的主说：我确是被压迫的，求你相助吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4857,
        "text": "我就以倾注的雨水开了许多天门，",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4858,
        "text": "我又使大地上的泉源涌出；雨水和泉水，就依既定的情状而汇合。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4859,
        "text": "我使他乘坐一只用木板和钉子制造的船上，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4860,
        "text": "在我的眷顾之下飘流，以报答被人否认者。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4861,
        "text": "我确已将这件事留作一种迹象，有接受劝告者吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4862,
        "text": "我的刑罚和警告是怎样的！",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4863,
        "text": "我确已使《古兰经》易于记诵，有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4864,
        "text": "阿德人否认过先知，我的刑罚和警告是怎样的！",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4865,
        "text": "我确已使暴风在一个很凶恶的日子去毁灭他们，",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4866,
        "text": "暴风将众人拔起，他们好象被拔出的海枣树干一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4867,
        "text": "我的刑罚和警告是怎样的！",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4868,
        "text": "我确已使《古兰经》易于记诵，有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4869,
        "text": "赛莫德人否认过警告，",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4870,
        "text": "故他们说：我们同族的一个凡人，我们能顺从他吗？如果那样，我们必定陷于迷误和疯狂之中。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4871,
        "text": "难道他在我们之间独自奉到启示吗？不然，他是说谎者，是傲慢者。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4872,
        "text": "他们明日将知道谁是说谎者，谁是傲慢者。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4873,
        "text": "我必定使母驼考验他们，故你应当期待他们，并应当坚忍，",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4874,
        "text": "你应当告诉他们，井水是他们和母驼所均分的，应得水分的，轮流着到井边来。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4875,
        "text": "他们曾喊来他们的朋友，他就拿起剑来宰了母驼。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4876,
        "text": "我的刑罚和警告是怎样的！",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4877,
        "text": "我确已使一种爆炸去毁灭他们，他们就变成造圈栏者所用的枯木。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4878,
        "text": "我确已使《古兰经》易于记诵，有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4879,
        "text": "鲁特的宗族曾否认警告，",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4880,
        "text": "我确已使飞沙走石的暴风去毁灭他们；惟鲁特的信徒，我在黎明时拯救了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4881,
        "text": "那是从我的主那里发出的恩典，我如此报酬感谢者。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4882,
        "text": "他确已将我的惩治警告他们，但他们以怀疑的态度否认警告。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4883,
        "text": "他们确已诱惑他，叫他不要保护他的客人，但我涂抹了他们的眼睛。你们尝试我的刑罚和警告吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4884,
        "text": "一种永恒的刑罚在早晨确已袭击了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4885,
        "text": "你们尝试我的刑罚和警告吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4886,
        "text": "我确已《古兰经》易于记诵，有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4887,
        "text": "警告确已降临法老的百姓，",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4888,
        "text": "他们否认了我的一切迹象，故我以万能者全能者的态度，惩治了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4889,
        "text": "你们中不信道的人们比这等人还优秀呢！还是天经中有关于你们的赦条呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4890,
        "text": "难道他们说：我们是一个常胜的团体。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4891,
        "text": "那个团体将败北，他们将转背。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4892,
        "text": "不然，复活时是他们的约期；复活时是更艰难的，是更辛苦的。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4893,
        "text": "犯罪者的确在迷误和烈火中。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4894,
        "text": "他们匍匐着被拖入火狱之日，将对他们说：你们尝试火狱的烧灼吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4895,
        "text": "我确已依定量而创造万物，",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4896,
        "text": "我的命令只是快如转瞬的一句话。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4897,
        "text": "我确已将你们的宗派毁灭了。有接受劝告的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4898,
        "text": "凡他们所做的事，都记载在天经中。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4899,
        "text": "一切小事和大事，都是被记录的。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4900,
        "text": "敬畏的人们，必定在乐园里，在光明中，",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4901,
        "text": "在全能的主那里，得居一个如意的地位。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
